  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dd2 \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0da7\u0dd0\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0da9\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dca\u0db4\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0db8\u0dad\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A Tiger fuel tank emerges from Pudukudirippu",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "During the war, a fuel tank which was buried in a private land in Pudukudirippu area of \u200b\u200bMullativu by the LTTE organization was excavated in front of Mullativu Magistrate R.Saravanaraja.",
        "The Pudukudirippu Police said that the fuel tank was discovered during the excavations carried out by the Pudukudirippu Police on the basis of an intelligence received by the Mullaitivu Army on the orders of the court.",
        "This fuel tank, which is 16.7 feet long and eight feet in diameter, has been revealed to be a fuel tank used to collect fuel needed by the LTTE organization during the last war.",
        "The police also mentioned that the fuel tank had been damaged due to being inside the ground for over 15 years and due to decay in some places.",
        "The Pudukudirippu Police, the Army and the Police Special Task Force carried out excavations using backhoes for several hours and after a lot of effort, they managed to bring the fuel tank to the surface of the ground.",
        "The magistrate also ordered the security forces to take the found fuel tank to the Pudukudirippu police station for further security."
      ],
